1.3.1	I'm no expert however, I suffered similar problems in that my comp, without warning, would switch itself off completely and then restart and boot to the welcome screen as if nothing had happened.	St
1.3.2	I persevered for around three months until I could take it no more.	St
1.3.3	I checked all my wiring connections inside my comp to start - no probs there!	St
1.3.4	I did a virus scan - no probs there!	St
1.3.5	I changed my RAM - still had the problem.	St
1.3.6	Then I changed my PSU from a FSP 250-60 GTA (250W) to a Jeantech 400W (30 from PC World) - Problem cured!!!	St
